This is my vim config. To use it, download pathogen and write the following
lines to your .vimrc:

let $MYVIMRC="$VIM/vimfiles/bundle/_vimrc"
source $MYVIMRC
call pathogen#infect()


Then use the following shell commands in your vimfiles/bundle to download
everything:

git init
git config core.autocrlf false
git remote add origin https://github.com/someboddy/vimConfig
git fetch
git checkout master
pullPlugins.bat

